default: Arc Share allows users to share files over local aera network, including photos, videos, music and any file that you want. All you need is Arc Share and web browser, and it's not required to install another client on your receiving devices. This app is beta version and it's functions are not fully completed. If you drop into any error, please contact the developer in the Settings tab or use Windows Feedback to contact me.
zh-cn: Arc Share 能够让用户在局域网之间传递文件，而不需任何流量连接，照片、视频、音乐以及任何你能想到的文件都可以。你只需要Arc Share和浏览器，并不需要在接收端设备额外安装多余的客户端。这个App目前还在测试阶段，一些功能并没有完成，所以使用过程中可能会遇到问题，请在设置栏联系开发者。
